{"tid":2312721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大將於中國大陸開辦三間分校 總投資307億元","createTime":"2020-12-05T08:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T11:16:18.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b00e2f6b67ad9ba3f70421b32a6cb5c4f65fcfb1","tid":2312721,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:00:01.000Z","msg":"在今年發布的《廣東省2020年重點建設前期預備項目計劃表》中，提及了佛山教育領域的多項建設情況，其中香港理工大學（佛山）建設項目被列入廣東省省2020年重點建設前期預備項目計劃。香港理工大學（佛山）建設項目計劃總投資307億元，建築面積約200萬平方米，將建設教學、實驗、科研、辦公、會議服務等用房、場館。<br />\n<br />\n佛山市和香港理工大學、廣州市合辦的香港理工大學廣佛校區簽約落地佛山三龍灣南海片區，校區選址&ldquo;中歐中心、世紀蓮&rdquo;、&ldquo;廣佛薈（林岳東地塊）&rdquo;、&ldquo;博智林機器人谷（群力圍地塊）&rdquo;，校園佔地面積合計3000餘畝。"},{"pid":"5e01f0cf851dfc3e6ea03688d9773f3df35f4028","tid":2312721,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qn4K1oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqn4K1oL.png&h=33c9db1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLzK1oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLzK1oL.png&h=bbe5027f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKicqQr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKicqQr.png&h=756d3cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5n1jar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5n1jar.jpg&h=3c9f3f43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bf6dc65365f0b1e976f8bb74a846edfe13e84e7","tid":2312721,"uid":178290,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"中國革命基地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ca877f6015fb5aad7aeceaa8d051f2d95fae9b","tid":2312721,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" cla